      "sourceLabels": [
        "Web source 2"
      ],
      "source": "https://www.floridavisiting.com/list/south-miami/"
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "text": "South Miami Heights sits 17 miles southwest of downtown Miami, making it a short drive into the heart of the city.",
